Package interfaces.services

package interfaces.services
The interface.services contains service interfaces defining various functionalities. Interfaces in this package represent contracts that service classes should implement.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0

    Description
    ApproveSuggestionServiceable
    The ApproveSuggestionServiceable interface defines a service for approving suggestions.
    AttendCampServiceable
    The AttendCampServiceable interface defines a service for attending camps that includes both registration and withdrawal capabilities.
    AuthServiceable
    The AuthServiceable interface defines a service for user authentication, encompassing both login and logout functionalities.
    CampServiceable
    The CampServiceable interface defines a service related to camp management, encompassing various forms and actions associated with camps.
    ChangePasswordServiceable
    The ChangePasswordServiceable interface defines a service for changing passwords.
    Creatable
    The Creatable interface defines a service for creating entities.
    DataServiceable
    The DataServiceable interface combines functionalities related to data handling, including importing and exporting data.

    The Deletable interface defines a method for deleting entities or data.
    Editable
    The Editable interface defines a method for editing entities or data.
    EnquiryServiceable
    The EnquiryServiceable interface defines methods related to handling enquiries.
    Exportable
    The Exportable interface defines a method for exporting data to a specified file path.
    Forms
    The Forms interface combines functionalities related to forms, including editing, creating, and deleting.
    GenerateReportServiceable
    The GenerateReportServiceable interface defines the functionality for generating reports related to a camp.

    The Importable interface represents an entity that can be imported from a specified file path.

    The SuggestionServiceable interface represents an entity that provides suggestion-related services and extends the Forms interface.
